@startuml
title System Architecture - Component Diagram

package "3D Image Generator" {
  [Input Parser] as Parser
  [Geometry Processor] as Geometry
  [Rendering Engine] as Renderer
  [Output Generator] as Output
  
  database "Data Models" as Data {
    [Point Cloud]
    [Mesh Data]
    [Scene Graph]
  }
}

package "External Libraries" {
  [OpenGL] as GL
  [GLFW] as GLFW
  [GLM] as GLM
  [stb_image] as STB
}

[User] --> Parser : Input files/config
Parser --> Data : Store parsed data
Geometry --> Data : Read/process data
Renderer --> Data : Access scene data
Renderer --> GL : Rendering calls
Renderer --> GLM : Math operations
Output --> STB : Image encoding
Renderer --> Output : Raw pixel data
Output --> [User] : Image files

note right of Parser
  Supports:
  - JSON config
  - OBJ/STL models
  - CSV point clouds
  - Text descriptions
end note

note right of Renderer
  Implements:
  - Transform pipeline
  - Lighting calculations
  - Material application
  - Post-processing
end note
@enduml